\sqrt{2x^2}\sqrt{2(6-x)^2}.
0 < x < 6
\sqrt{2x^2}=\sqrt{2}\;x
\sqrt{2(6-x)^2}=\sqrt{2}\;(6-x)
A(x)
A(x)=2x(6-x).
\sqrt{a^2}=|a|
\sqrt{2}|6-x|
0 \le x \le 6
|6-x|=6-x
b^2=2(6-x)^2 \Rightarrow b=\sqrt{2}(6-x)
a^2=2x^2 \Rightarrow a=\sqrt{2}x
A=ab \Rightarrow A=2(6x-x^2)\Rightarrow A'_x=2(6-2x)
A'_x=0\Rightarrow x=3 \Rightarrow A=18
